EN: In the celebration, balloons were released into the sky.

ZH: 她在生日宴会上得了一个气球作为奖品。
EN: She won a balloon as a prize at the birthday party.

ZH: 这只气球已经泄漏了。
EN: This balloon has deflated.

ZH: 我们需要一支气球泵来给气球充气。
EN: We need a balloon pump to inflate the balloons.

ZH: 学校门口挂着很多漂亮的气球。
EN: There are many beautiful balloons hanging at the school gate.

ZH: 她抓住了气球的线，不让它飞走。
EN: She held onto the string of the balloon so it wouldn't fly away.
